Kinect AS3 Experiments using TUIO and UDP-Flash Bridge

SETUP
1 - Checkout the project in your system
2 - Inside FDT just import the existing project
3 - Have fun!

HOW TO RUN
1 - Open the TuioKinect.app inside the libs folder
2 - run the socket inside the folder "libs/udp-flashlc-bridge"
3 - Publish the SWF
4 - Have more fun!

CONCEPT EXAMPLE
http://silviopaganini.posterous.com/openkinect-flash-tuio-udp-flash-bridge